#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:551
msgid ""
"Select the PayPal logo style displayed next to the payment method title on "
"the checkout page."
msgstr ""
"Velg PayPal-logoen som vises ved siden av betalingsmetodetittelen på "
"kassesiden."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:554
msgid "Show Redirect Icon and Text"
msgstr "Vis omdirigeringsikon og tekst"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:558
msgid ""
"When enabled, a redirect icon and message will appear to let customers know "
"they will be taken to PayPal to complete their payment."
msgstr ""
"Når aktivert, vil et omdirigeringsikon og en melding vises for å informere "
"kundene om at de vil bli tatt til PayPal for å fullføre betalingen."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:561
msgid "Use Place Order Button"
msgstr "Bruk Bestillingsknappen"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:565
msgid ""
"Enable this to use the default Place Order button on the checkout page "
"instead of showing PayPal buttons. This setting does not affect Express "
"Checkout."
msgstr ""
"Aktiver dette for å bruke standard \"Plasser ordre\"-knappen på kassesiden i "
"stedet for å vise PayPal-knapper. Denne innstillingen påvirker ikke Express "
"Checkout."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:713
msgid ""
"To use Advanced Card Payments, ensure your PayPal account is eligible and "
"enabled:<br><br>1. Visit developer.paypal.com → Apps & Credentials → API "
"Credentials.<br>2. Click your App Name.<br>3. Under \"Features\" → Accept "
"Payments, check if \"Advanced Credit and Debit Card Payments\" is enabled."
"<br>4. If missing, your account or region may not support it."
msgstr ""
"For å bruke Advanced Card Payments, må du sørge for at PayPal-kontoen din er "
"kvalifisert og aktivert:<br><br>1. Besøk developer.paypal.com → Apps & "
"Credentials → API Credentials.<br>2. Klikk på App-navnet ditt.<br>3. Under "
"\"Features\" → Accept Payments, sjekk om \"Advanced Credit and Debit Card "
"Payments\" er aktivert.<br>4. Hvis det mangler, kan det hende at kontoen din "
"eller regionen din ikke støtter det."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:734
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:792
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:816
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1058
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1080
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1116
#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:1367
msgid "Important Note"
msgstr "Viktig merknad"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:741
msgid "Enable Advanced Credit/Debit Card"
msgstr "Aktiver avansert kreditt-/debetkort"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:743
msgid ""
"Enable the Advanced Credit/Debit Card payment option as a separate gateway on "
"the checkout page. This gateway typically offers a lower PayPal fee compared "
"to the PayPal Smart Button. The fee is 2.59% + $0.49* per transaction for "
"Advanced Credit/Debit Card payments and 3.49% + $0.49* for PayPal Smart "
"Buttons. It supports major cards like Visa, Mastercard, and American Express, "
"providing a secure and streamlined payment experience."
msgstr ""
"Aktiver alternativet for avansert kreditt-/debetkortbetaling som en egen "
"betalingsløsning på kassesiden. Denne betalingsløsningen tilbyr vanligvis et "
"lavere PayPal-gebyr sammenlignet med PayPal Smart Button. Gebyret er 2,59 % + "
"$0,49* per transaksjon for avanserte kreditt-/debetkortbetalinger og 3,49 % + "
"$0,49* for PayPal Smart Buttons. Den støtter store kort som Visa, Mastercard "
"og American Express, og gir en sikker og strømlinjeformet betalingsopplevelse."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:749
msgid ""
"Set the title for the Advanced Credit/Debit Card payment method as it will "
"appear on the checkout page (e.g., 'Pay with Credit/Debit Card').."
msgstr ""
"Sett tittelen for betalingsmetoden for avansert kreditt-/debetkort som den "
"vil vises på utsjekkingssiden (f.eks. 'Betal med kreditt-/debetkort')."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:750
msgid "Credit or Debit Card"
msgstr "Kreditt- eller debetkort"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:754
msgid "Disable specific credit cards"
msgstr "Deaktiver spesifikke kredittkort"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:760
msgid ""
"By default all possible credit cards will be accepted. You can disable some "
"cards, if you wish."
msgstr ""
"Som standard vil alle mulige kredittkort bli akseptert. Du kan deaktivere "
"noen kort hvis du ønsker det."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:767
msgid "Contingency for 3D Secure"
msgstr "Beredskap for 3D Secure"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:771
msgid "3D Secure when required"
msgstr "3D Secure når det er nødvendig"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:772
msgid "Always trigger 3D Secure"
msgstr "Alltid utløse 3D Secure"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:776
msgid ""
"3D Secure benefits cardholders and merchants by providing an additional layer "
"of verification using Verified by Visa, MasterCard SecureCode and American "
"Express SafeKey."
msgstr ""
"3D Secure gir fordeler til kortinnehavere og handelsmenn ved å tilby et "
"ekstra lag med verifisering ved hjelp av Verified by Visa, MasterCard "
"SecureCode og American Express SafeKey."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:779
msgid "Card Save Enabled"
msgstr "Kortlagring aktivert"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:780
msgid "Enable card saving at checkout"
msgstr "Aktiver kortlagring ved utsjekking"

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:783
msgid ""
"When enabled, customers can securely save their card details using PayPal for "
"faster future checkouts."
msgstr ""
"Når aktivert, kan kunder trygt lagre kortdetaljene sine ved hjelp av PayPal "
"for raskere fremtidige utsjekkinger."

#: ppcp/includes/class-ppcp-paypal-checkout-for-woocommerce-settings.php:794
msgid ""
"Advanced Credit/Debit Card payments are not enabled in your PayPal account. "
"<br><br><strong>Supported Countries:</strong><br>Australia, Austria, Belgium, "
